<reference id="class_snapshotconfig">
    <title><ph keyref="SnapshotConfig"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">用于配置截图功能。</ph></shortdesc>
    <refbody>
        <section id="prototype">
            <p outputclass="codeblock">
            <codeblock props="android" outputclass="language-java">public class SnapshotConfig {
  public String filePath = null;
  public Constants.VideoModulePosition position = Constants.VideoModulePosition.VIDEO_MODULE_POSITION_PRE_ENCODER;
}</codeblock>
            <codeblock props="hmos" outputclass="language-arkts"/>
            <codeblock props="ios mac" outputclass="language-objectivec">@interface AgoraSnapshotConfig: NSObject
@property (copy, nonatomic) NSString * _Nullable filePath;
@property(assign, nonatomic) AgoraVideoModulePosition position;
@end</codeblock>
            <codeblock props="cpp unreal" outputclass="language-cpp">struct SnapshotConfig {
  const char* filePath;
  media::base::VIDEO_MODULE_POSITION position;
  SnapshotConfig() :filePath(NULL), position(media::base::POSITION_PRE_ENCODER) {}
};</codeblock>
            <codeblock props="bp" outputclass="language-cpp"/>
            <codeblock props="electron" outputclass="language-typescript"/>
            <codeblock props="unity cs" outputclass="language-csharp"/>
            <codeblock props="rn" outputclass="language-typescript"/>
            <codeblock props="flutter" outputclass="language-dart"/> </p>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <dl outputclass="since">
            <dlentry props="native">
                <dt>自从：</dt>
                <dd>自 vx.x.x 版本新增。</dd>
                </dlentry>
            </dl>
            <p>该结构体用于设置截图的保存路径和视频观测的位置。</p>
            </section>
        <section id="parameters">
            <title><text conref="../conref/conref_api_metadata.dita#conref_api_metadata/property"/></title>
            <parml>
            <plentry props="android cpp ios">
                <pt props="android cpp ios">filePath</pt>
                <pd props="android">截图的本地路径（包含文件扩展名）。</pd>
                <pd props="ios">截图文件的保存路径。</pd>
                <pd props="cpp">截图的本地路径（包含文件扩展名）。例如：
                    <ul>
                        <li>Windows：<ph keyref="imagePath-example"/></li>
                        <li>iOS：<codeph>/App Sandbox/Library/Caches/example.jpg</codeph></li>
                        <li>macOS：<ph keyref="imagePath-example"/></li>
                        <li>Android：<codeph>/storage/emulated/0/Android/data/&lt;package name&gt;/files/example.jpg</codeph>。</li>
                        </ul>
                    </pd>
            </plentry>
            <plentry props="android cpp ios">
                <pt props="android cpp ios">position</pt>
                <pd props="android">视频观测的位置，详见 <xref keyref="VIDEO_MODULE_POSITION"/>。</pd>
                <pd props="ios">截图的模块位置，详见 <xref keyref="VIDEO_MODULE_POSITION"/>。</pd>
                <pd props="cpp">视频观测的位置，详见 <xref keyref="VIDEO_MODULE_POSITION"/>。
                    <ul>
                        <li>当 <codeph>uid = 0</codeph> 时，支持的位置为 2、4 和 8。</li>
                        <li>当 <codeph>uid ≠ 0</codeph> 时，仅支持位置 2。</li>
                        </ul>
                    </pd>
            </plentry>
            </parml> </section>
            </refbody>
